#X text 543 248 The [gatehold~] object holds (or 'delays') a gate value for a certain amount of time (specified in ms) after the gate has closed. On the other hand \, [gaterelease~] releases a gate value after a given amount of time (specified in ms) after the gate has opened. [trighold~] holds the value of an impulse or gate Check the help files.;
